{"tid":2193892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇香港人依幾年 一年比一年絕望","createTime":"2020-09-08T07:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T09:29:57.000Z","uid":42246,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"20feb56e1792c67ae6849fdd0b960d8de9c9a76e","tid":2193892,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"大家識規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友 90後 畢業做野幾年<br />\n由17年開始 呀婆病左同18年年尾走<br />\n20幾歲第一次有咁親既人離開自己<br />\n發現離別真係好痛好唔真實<br />\n<br />\n點知19年反送中 成個香港唔同曬<br />\n發生既事我諗我日後上天堂同呀婆講返佢一定會以為我吹水<br />\n由自己一家唔開心 變成全港唔開心<br />\n<br />\n到2020 武肺 經濟差 <br />\n國安法判香港死刑 香港正式對外宣布香港唔係香港<br />\n自己打份牛工 餓你唔死 但一定向唔到上流<br />\n叫做有返工既廢青 <br />\n女就唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家好低慾望 十足十日本既低慾社會例子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個未來一年絕望過一年<br />\n最恐怖係90後開始30歲<br />\n00後都20歲 唔可以同自己講重係18 22<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有本bno 有20萬儲蓄 既90後覺得0希望"},{"pid":"9adf86eb7ac8480303e47ddae37f73cca1c21c86","tid":2193892,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c993124da96b03c4cdbd468f95700492deeb422","tid":2193892,"uid":302578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"咁冇bno嘅我係咪可以去自殺"},{"pid":"35e4852e8ab979822d031a713cbd419721e09d83","tid":2193892,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"d4a6cfc1e0aa852ac8b36e387116e0f9f47e8893","tid":2193892,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c993124da96b03c4cdbd468f95700492deeb422","tid":2193892,"uid":302578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"咁冇bno嘅我係咪可以去自殺"},"citedBy":1,"repl